      • isDoFilter

        default boolean isDoFilter(java.lang.String propertyName)
        If the return value is True, the operation will be released. (The operation will be executed.) If the return value is False, the operation will be rejected. (The operation will not be processed.)
        参数:
        propertyName - Parameter names for filtering or not
        返回:
        true:can operation;false:Not filtered (not operated)
